    "It underscores the need for ethical considerations to be deeply embedded in healthcare practices, including the use of generative AI technologies.",
    "The UK's approach to healthcare ethics, particularly in the context of generative AI, involves scrutinizing the impact of generative AI on healthcare relationships and ensuring that the development and deployment of generative AI are aligned with the fundamental principles of medical ethics.",
    "Legal and Regulatory FrameworkThe legal and regulatory framework in the UK for generative AI in healthcare is characterized by an effort to adapt to the rapid advancements in generative AI and ML technologies.",
